        <img src="~/images/pexels-malkocogluraw-18058021.jpg" alt="About Our Company">
        <p><strong>Who are we and what do we offer?</strong></p>
        <p>Welcome to KhumaloCraft, where passion meets craftsmanship. Founded by James Khumalo, KhumaloCraft is a premier e-commerce platform dedicated to showcasing the beauty of handcrafted treasures.</p>
        <button onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("ContactUs", "Home")'">Contact Us</button>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

