    <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <img src="~/images/pexels-cottonbro-3778080.jpg" alt="Our Story">
        <p>James Khumalo established KhumaloCraft with a vision to create a global community for handmade products. Inspired by the rich cultural heritage of craftsmanship. We strive to give South African artists a platform to promote and hopefully sell their artworks. We encourage customers and artists to reach out to one another to achieve a valued service to both parties.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- Our Mission Section -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <img src="~/images/pottery-1139047_640.jpg" alt="Our Mission">
